reviews.review_text: The best SBD for this show Surprisingly, the Charlie Miller SBD for this show is not the best source. This one sounds much cleaner and the instrument levels are less tinny and more balanced. '85 has some spotty tapes, so when one like this pops up, it is a real treat.
